data.description: Welcome home to this charming home in Madison Village! Easily entertain in your eat-in kitchen while preparing meals or relax in the living room in front of the pellet stove during the colder months! The first floor offers 2 generous size bedrooms, a fully updated bathroom and a laundry room. Upstairs you will find a large bathroom and bedroom as well. Your backyard is fully fenced in for privacy and offers a patio for entertaining or relaxing nights! Hardwood floors throughout that were recently refinished, new roof, newer furnace and AC. Located close to parks, shopping and restaurants. Call today to schedule your private showing, you won't want to miss this home! VIRTUAL TOUR:
